    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V26",
    "versetext": "तत्रा पश्यत्स्थितान्पार्थः पितॄनथ पितामहान् । \nआचार्यान्मातुलान्भ्रातॄन्पुत्रान्पौत्रान्सखींस्तथा ॥ २६ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V27",
    "versetext": "श्वशुरान्सुहृदश्चैवसेनयोरुभयोरपि । \nता न्समीक्ष्य स कौन्तेयः सर्वान्बन्धूनवस्थितान् ॥ २७ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V28",
    "versetext": "कृपया परयाविष्टो विषीदन्निदमब्रवीत् । \nअर्जुन उवाच — \nदृष्ट्वे मान्स्वजनान्कृष्ण युयुत्सून्समुपस्थितान् ॥ २८ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V29",
    "versetext": "सीदन्ति मम गात्राणि मुखं च परिशुष्यति । \nवेपथुश्च शरीरे मे रोमहर्षश्च जायते ॥ २९ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V30",
    "versetext": "गाण्डीवं स्रंसते हस्तात्त्वक्चैव परिदह्यते । \nन च शक्नोम्यवस्थातुं भ्रमतीव च मे मनः ॥ ३० ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V31",
    "versetext": "निमित्तानि च पश्यामि विपरीतानि केशव । \nन च श्रेयोऽनुपश्यामि हत्वा स्वजनमाहवे ॥ ३१ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V32",
    "versetext": "न काङ्क्षे विजयं कृष्ण न च राज्यं सुखानि च । \nकिं नो राज्येन गोविन्द किं भोगैर्जीवितेन वा ॥ ३२ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V33",
    "versetext": "येषा मर्थे काङ्क्षितं नो राज्यं भोगाः सुखानि च । \nत इमेऽवस्थिता युद्धे प्राणांस्त्यक्त्वा धनानि च ॥ ३३ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V34",
    "versetext": "आचार्याः पितरः पुत्रास्तथैव च पितामहाः । \nमातुलाः श्वशुराः पौत्राः स्यालाः सम्बन्धिनस्तथा ॥ ३४ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V35",
    "versetext": "एता न्न हन्तुमिच्छामि घ्नतोऽपि मधुसूदन । \nअपि त्रैलोक्यराज्यस्य हेतोः किं नु महीकृते ॥ ३५ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V36",
    "versetext": "निहत्य धार्तराष्ट्रान्नः का प्रीतिः स्याज्जनार्दन । \nपापमेवा श्रयेदस्मान्हत्वैतानाततायिनः ॥ ३६ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V37",
    "versetext": "तस्मा न्नार्हा वयं हन्तुं धार्तराष्ट्रान्सबान्धवान् । \nस्वजनं हि कथं हत्वा सुखिनः स्याम माधव ॥ ३७ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V38",
    "versetext": "यद्य प्येते न पश्यन्ति लोभोपहतचेतसः । \nकुलक्षयकृतं दोषं मित्रद्रोहे च पातकम् ॥ ३८ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V39",
    "versetext": "कथं न ज्ञेयमस्माभिः पापादस्मान्निवर्तितुम् । \nकुलक्षयकृतं दोषं प्रपश्यद्भिर्जनार्दन ॥ ३९ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V40",
    "versetext": "कुल क्षये प्रणश्यन्ति कुलधर्माः सनातनाः । \nधर्मे नष्टे कुलं कृत्स्नमधर्मोऽभिभवत्युत ॥ ४० ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V41",
    "versetext": "अधर्मा भिभवात्कृष्ण प्रदुष्यन्ति कुलस्त्रियः । \nस्त्रीषु दुष्टासु वार्ष्णेय जायते वर्णसङ्करः ॥ ४१ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V42",
    "versetext": "सङ्करो नरकायैव कुलघ्नानां कुलस्य च । \nपतन्ति पितरो ह्येषां लुप्त पिण्डोदकक्रियाः ॥ ४२ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V43",
    "versetext": "दोषै रेतैः कुलघ्नानां वर्णसङ्करकारकैः । \nउत्साद्यन्ते जातिधर्माः कुलधर्माश्च शाश्वताः ॥ ४३ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
    ],
    "citations": []
  },
  {
    "source_url": "https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari",
    "source_sha256": "39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912",
    "chapter_id": "BG_C01",
    "verse_id": "BG_C01_V44",
    "versetext": "उत्सन्न कुलधर्माणां मनुष्याणां जनार्दन । \nनरके नियतं वासो भवतीत्य नुशुश्रुम ॥ ४४ ॥",
    "leading_bhashya": "",
    "bhashya_blocks": [],
    "source_block_types_present": [
      "versetext"
    ],
    "record_kinds_present": [
      "sutra"
